00:20:40,950 --> 00:20:41,720
Amazing.

604
00:20:42,950 --> 00:20:44,750
Come back when you hit that side.

605
00:20:44,790 --> 00:20:45,470
Okay.

606
00:20:46,030 --> 00:20:47,190
How have you been?

