633
00:21:27,540 --> 00:21:28,510
Aren't you also lucky?

634
00:21:28,510 --> 00:21:29,630
You have me as a friend.

635
00:21:29,630 --> 00:21:30,270
Yes, that's right.

636
00:21:30,270 --> 00:21:30,990
You also got me that motorcycle.

637
00:21:30,990 --> 00:21:32,070
Yeah.

638
00:21:33,790 --> 00:21:35,910
Many thanks for the wonderful speech

639
00:21:35,930 --> 00:21:38,260
brought by the queen of air conditioners.

640
00:21:38,310 --> 00:21:38,830
Next up,

641
00:21:38,850 --> 00:21:39,970
we'll be joined by

