00:21:44,110 --> 00:21:45,550
as a best-selling author,

646
00:21:45,550 --> 00:21:46,790
a blog writer,

647
00:21:46,950 --> 00:21:49,290
and an elite woman who excels in

648
00:21:49,510 --> 00:21:50,750
balancing home life and career.

649
00:21:50,750 --> 00:21:52,680
Now, let's give a round of applause

650
00:21:52,870 --> 00:21:53,680
to Ms. Cherry

651
00:21:53,830 --> 00:21:55,890
