652
00:21:59,720 --> 00:22:00,520
Good afternoon, everyone.

653
00:22:00,520 --> 00:22:01,290
I am Cherry.

654
00:22:05,000 --> 00:22:05,450
I...

655
00:22:06,090 --> 00:22:07,750
I'm really nervous right now.

656
00:22:11,150 --> 00:22:12,670
I-I actually wrote a script

657
00:22:12,670 --> 00:22:13,330
for this speech.

658
00:22:13,330 --> 00:22:14,330
I put a lot of effort into it

659
00:22:14,330 --> 00:22:16,260
and wrote several thousand words.

660
00:22:16,590 --> 00:22:18,150
But now I-I-I...

661
00:22:18,340 --> 00:22:20,070
I can't remember a single word.

662
00:22:21,220 --> 00:22:23,280
Well, if you would kindly lend an ear,

663
00:22:23,620 --> 00:22:25,230
I'll share with you

664
00:22:25,250 --> 00:22:27,090
a recent story in my life.

665
00:22:27,690 --> 00:22:29,000
A couple of months ago,

666
00:22:29,310 --> 00:22:31,740
I was a stay-at-home mother

667
00:22:31,760 --> 00:22:33,360
and an online writer.

668
00:22:34,330 --> 00:22:36,090
My husband was a programmer.

669
00:22:36,120 --> 00:22:37,470
He was busy at work.

670
00:22:37,780 --> 00:22:38,950
But now,

671
00:22:39,230 --> 00:22:40,830
he is a stay-at-home dad,

672
00:22:41,470 --> 00:22:43,150
while I've started building a business.

673
00:22:43,150 --> 00:22:45,470
So, for now,

674
00:22:45,750 --> 00:22:47,280
I have to leave him in charge

675
00:22:47,470 --> 00:22:49,750
of the whole housekeeping and parenting stuff.

676
00:22:49,750 --> 00:22:50,890
Of course, I embraced myself

677
00:22:50,890 --> 00:22:52,130
for his complaints.

678
00:22:53,470 --> 00:22:54,790
What I didn't expect was,

679
00:22:54,790 --> 00:22:56,120
some time ago, he told me

680
00:22:56,390 --> 00:22:57,990
that he didn't regret making

681
00:22:58,350 --> 00:22:59,590
this decision with me.

682
00:22:59,590 --> 00:23:01,120
He isn't worried or nervous

683
00:23:01,350 --> 00:23:01,960
because

684
00:23:02,550 --> 00:23:04,670
he still has chances to make money in the future

685
00:23:04,670 --> 00:23:05,710
and he feels the need

686
00:23:05,710 --> 00:23:07,110
to spend time with our son

687
00:23:07,590 --> 00:23:09,320
before the little guy grows up.

688
00:23:09,750 --> 00:23:11,280
Mothers tend to

689
00:23:11,310 --> 00:23:12,950
tell their children

690
00:23:13,120 --> 00:23:14,320
not to do this or that,

691
00:23:14,430 --> 00:23:15,980
while fathers might

692
00:23:16,000 --> 00:23:17,160
communicate with the children

693
00:23:17,160 --> 00:23:18,280
in a different way.

694
00:23:19,350 --> 00:23:20,590
Not long ago, my son

695
00:23:20,590 --> 00:23:22,270
saw my husband drinking coffee

696
00:23:22,270 --> 00:23:23,670
and he insisted on having some.

697
00:23:23,670 --> 00:23:24,430
Being faced with that,

698
00:23:24,430 --> 00:23:25,180
I would tell my son

699
00:23:25,180 --> 00:23:25,970
that he couldn't drink it,

700
00:23:25,970 --> 00:23:27,060
and then I'd reason with him,

701
00:23:27,060 --> 00:23:28,170
explaining why he couldn't.

702
00:23:28,170 --> 00:23:29,570
He could cry all he wanted

703
00:23:29,630 --> 00:23:30,610
but there's no way I would

704
00:23:30,610 --> 00:23:32,070
let him drink black coffee.

705
00:23:32,070 --> 00:23:32,950
But here's

706
00:23:33,020 --> 00:23:34,490
how my husband dealt with it.

707
00:23:34,490 --> 00:23:36,150
He looked at our son and asked,

708
00:23:36,270 --> 00:23:37,710
"Do you really want to drink it?

709
00:23:37,710 --> 00:23:38,550
I'm telling you,

710
00:23:38,550 --> 00:23:39,230
this doesn't taste good.

711
00:23:39,230 --> 00:23:40,960
You still wanna try it, right?"

712
00:23:41,000 --> 00:23:42,070
Our son nodded.

713
00:23:42,500 --> 00:23:43,750
Then he took a big sip.

714
00:23:44,140 --> 00:23:45,340
He pursed his lips and cried,

715
00:23:45,340 --> 00:23:46,940
saying, "This is so bitter!"

716
00:23:47,030 --> 00:23:47,800
From then on,

717
00:23:47,830 --> 00:23:49,190
he has never made the same request

718
00:23:49,190 --> 00:23:50,430
to my husband again.

719
00:23:50,540 --> 00:23:53,600
Also, thanks to what my husband did, our son didn't cry.

720
00:23:53,950 --> 00:23:54,870
Anyway,

721
00:23:55,710 --> 00:23:56,550
today,

722
00:23:56,850 --> 00:23:58,800
what I most want to share with you

723
00:23:59,830 --> 00:24:01,830
is my respect for my husband,

724
00:24:02,590 --> 00:24:03,500
and my deepest gratitude

725
00:24:03,500 --> 00:24:05,680
for what he has done for me in recent days.

726
00:24:05,680 --> 00:24:07,670
I think of it

727
00:24:07,700 --> 00:24:10,670
as the most useful and wonderful gift I've received

728
00:24:11,150 --> 00:24:12,160
in this year.

729
00:24:13,070 --> 00:24:13,730
Certainly,

730
00:24:13,790 --> 00:24:15,200
I won't just leave him

731
00:24:15,220 --> 00:24:16,830
with all the responsibilities.

732
00:24:16,830 --> 00:24:18,120
A child's growth

733
00:24:18,150 --> 00:24:19,400
requires the participation

734
00:24:19,400 --> 00:24:20,350
of both parents.

735
00:24:20,790 --> 00:24:22,710
I've decided, after this talk,

736
00:24:23,000 --> 00:24:24,170
I'll go home

737
00:24:24,310 --> 00:24:25,870
and spend some quality time with my son.

738
00:24:25,870 --> 00:24:26,860
Thank you.

739
00:24:38,550 --> 00:24:38,900
Honey,

740
00:24:38,900 --> 00:24:40,540
