741
00:24:40,540 --> 00:24:42,030
I want a video chat with our son.

742
00:24:42,030 --> 00:24:43,290
What are you doing now?

743
00:24:48,060 --> 00:24:50,230
Hello, Meng Feifei.

744
00:24:50,600 --> 00:24:52,140
Judging from your tone,

745
00:24:52,300 --> 00:24:54,230
