00:24:54,470 --> 00:24:55,310
Not really.

747
00:24:55,590 --> 00:24:57,850
I forgot my speech when I got on the stage.

748
00:24:58,070 --> 00:24:59,800
T-Then what happened?

749
00:25:00,310 --> 00:25:01,490
The whole thing fell apart?

750
00:25:01,490 --> 00:25:02,670
As I was on the stage,

751
00:25:02,690 --> 00:25:03,350
I saw

752
00:25:03,370 --> 00:25:05,000
