753
00:25:05,030 --> 00:25:05,960
I was so worried.

754
00:25:06,830 --> 00:25:08,020
Out of sheer desperation,

755
00:25:08,020 --> 00:25:09,210
I could do nothing but tell them

756
00:25:09,210 --> 00:25:10,670
a story about how Zhou Quan

757
00:25:10,870 --> 00:25:12,070
takes care of our son.

758
00:25:12,510 --> 00:25:13,190
I haven't

759
00:25:13,390 --> 00:25:14,720
