760
00:25:15,860 --> 00:25:18,460
That's all you shared with them?

761
00:25:19,100 --> 00:25:20,830
The audience liked it, I guess,

762
00:25:21,070 --> 00:25:22,490
because when I got off the stage,

763
00:25:22,490 --> 00:25:24,390
