768
00:25:29,440 --> 00:25:31,240
That's great!

769
00:25:32,110 --> 00:25:33,110
Gosh!

770
00:25:33,630 --> 00:25:34,990
Never have I felt

771
00:25:35,010 --> 00:25:36,240
