1128
00:36:42,990 --> 00:36:43,860
Tell me about it.

1129
00:36:43,860 --> 00:36:44,830
Did you resign?

1130
00:36:44,910 --> 00:36:45,610
At least I didn't

1131
00:36:45,610 --> 00:36:46,610
