00:38:14,620 --> 00:38:16,410
You're just a little boy now.

1150
00:38:17,070 --> 00:38:17,850
If you feel pain,

1151
00:38:17,850 --> 00:38:19,190
you can cry in front of Mommy.

1152
00:38:19,190 --> 00:38:19,910
It's okay.

1153
00:38:20,150 --> 00:38:21,630
I'm not a little boy.

1154
00:38:21,660 --> 00:38:23,030
I'm a man.

1155
00:38:25,950 --> 00:38:26,750
Daddy said so.

1156
00:38:27,040 --> 00:38:28,700
Yeah. That's what Daddy said.

1157
00:38:34,200 --> 00:38:35,360
Mommy is so sorry.

1158
00:38:35,900 --> 00:38:37,870
It's not your fault that I fell.

1159
00:38:38,630 --> 00:38:39,450
But still, I failed

1160
00:38:39,450 --> 00:38:40,780
