00:38:45,540 --> 00:38:47,260
He failed to take good care of you.

1164
00:38:47,260 --> 00:38:49,260
He has been doing great.

1165
00:38:52,270 --> 00:38:53,130
Where is Daddy?

1166
00:38:54,600 --> 00:38:56,260
He went home to get something.

1167
00:38:56,520 --> 00:38:57,920
He'll be back in a moment.

1168
00:39:01,270 --> 00:39:01,990
Do you really think

1169
00:39:01,990 --> 00:39:04,120
Daddy has been taking good care of you?

1170
00:39:04,150 --> 00:39:04,710
Yes.

1171
00:39:05,110 --> 00:39:07,030
Daddy and I have had so much fun.

1172
00:39:07,480 --> 00:39:09,920
All we've played is men's games.

1173
00:39:10,510 --> 00:39:12,030
I'm so happy.

1174
00:39:12,480 --> 00:39:13,330
Mommy, I think

1175
00:39:13,360 --> 00:39:14,970
