1176
00:39:20,620 --> 00:39:21,940
I should praise Daddy.

1177
00:39:35,770 --> 00:39:37,080
I have a question.

1178
00:39:37,270 --> 00:39:38,630
I'm sorry to bother you.

1179
00:39:38,780 --> 00:39:39,820
This ointment

1180
00:39:40,200 --> 00:39:42,490
is for the wound, right?

1181
00:39:42,930 --> 00:39:44,030
I-If I put a bit more

1182
00:39:44,070 --> 00:39:45,270
on the wound every day,

1183
00:39:45,270 --> 00:39:47,270
will it prevent scars from forming?

1184
00:39:47,350 --> 00:39:48,920
You should ask the doctor

1185
00:39:48,940 --> 00:39:50,630
if there will be a scar.

1186
00:39:52,850 --> 00:39:54,860
Okay. Sorry for bothering you.

1187
00:39:54,930 --> 00:39:55,530
Thank you.

1188
00:39:55,560 --> 00:39:56,250
Thank you.

1189
00:40:00,120 --> 00:40:02,060
Mommy is my favorite.

1190
00:40:02,470 --> 00:40:04,710
Daddy comes second.

1191
00:40:05,150 --> 00:40:07,310
He's followed by Grandma.

1192
00:40:08,180 --> 00:40:09,050
Didn't Grandma use to be

1193
00:40:09,050 --> 00:40:10,190
your second favorite?

1194
00:40:10,190 --> 00:40:10,910
Why is she

1195
00:40:10,940 --> 00:40:12,370
in the third place now?

1196
00:40:12,830 --> 00:40:15,430
I've been having so much fun with Daddy lately.

1197
00:40:15,670 --> 00:40:17,800
Plus, now I can eat

1198
00:40:17,820 --> 00:40:18,880
and sleep on my own

1199
00:40:19,120 --> 00:40:20,930
without Grandma's help.

1200
00:40:22,970 --> 00:40:24,110
Aiwen, listen,

1201
00:40:24,640 --> 00:40:25,840
Mommy is happy

1202
00:40:25,860 --> 00:40:27,000
to be your favorite,

1203
00:40:27,670 --> 00:40:28,550
but

1204
00:40:28,550 --> 00:40:30,310
what you said is wrong.

1205
00:40:31,130 --> 00:40:32,390
You can't like someone

1206
00:40:32,550 --> 00:40:34,830
just because they'd do certain things

1207
00:40:35,090 --> 00:40:36,710
for you.

1208
00:40:37,190 --> 00:40:39,050
That will make you a utilitarian.

1209
00:40:39,230 --> 00:40:41,360
Do you know what "utilitarian" means?

1210
00:40:41,550 --> 00:40:42,520
You don't. It's okay.

1211
00:40:42,520 --> 00:40:44,390
You'll understand when you get older.

1212
00:40:44,390 --> 00:40:46,030
Mommy just wants to tell you

1213
00:40:46,400 --> 00:40:47,760
that I, your daddy

1214
00:40:47,790 --> 00:40:48,730
and your grandparents

1215
00:40:48,730 --> 00:40:50,210
all love you dearly

1216
00:40:50,520 --> 00:40:52,400
because we are family.

1217
00:40:53,260 --> 00:40:54,740
You should love them too.

1218
00:40:55,430 --> 00:40:56,310
Do not try to

1219
00:40:56,360 --> 00:40:57,640
rank them,

1220
00:40:58,350 --> 00:40:59,060
okay?

1221
00:41:00,500 --> 00:41:01,190
Okay.

1222
00:41:01,220 --> 00:41:02,540
But I still like

1223
00:41:03,280 --> 00:41:04,550
you and Daddy the best.

1224
00:41:06,260 --> 00:41:08,740
Grandma always tells me not to

1225
00:41:08,770 --> 00:41:09,730
do this or that.

1226
00:41:10,300 --> 00:41:11,380
That's the way

1227
00:41:11,400 --> 00:41:12,930
Grandma shows care for you.

1228
00:41:13,070 --> 00:41:13,920
If you don't like it,

1229
00:41:13,920 --> 00:41:15,650
you should talk to her about it.

1230
00:41:15,860 --> 00:41:17,290
Just don't say

1231
00:41:17,340 --> 00:41:18,750
you dislike her

1232
00:41:19,020 --> 00:41:21,440
because she wouldn't do certain things for you.

1233
00:41:21,440 --> 00:41:22,760
That is absolutely wrong.

1234
00:41:22,760 --> 00:41:23,370
Right?

1235
00:41:24,590 --> 00:41:25,230
Right.

1236
00:41:25,680 --> 00:41:27,690
Great. Good boy.

1237
00:42:37,110 --> 00:42:38,550
Today, Aiwen said to me,

1238
00:42:40,710 --> 00:42:41,470
"Mommy,

1239
00:42:42,510 --> 00:42:43,970
you should praise Daddy."
